00081 // Various styles of connect possible
00082 // Note that there is only one option right now.  When additional options appear, we can choose if the
00083 // options should be exclusive (only one value passed) or can be combined (or'ed together).  That will
00084 // change what subsequent values of enum options should be (1,2,3,4 vs 1,2,4,8)
00085 typedef enum GTI_CONNECT_OPTIONS_T
00086 {
00087     CONNECT_OPT_LEGACY = 0,     // Default connect
00088     CONNECT_OPT_SACI = 1        // Connect in SACI mode, which is a explicit to loki devices
00089 } GTI_CONNECT_OPTIONS;
